WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:13.000
Take your new Bebop camera

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Take your PH8 screwdriver

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:18.000
Take a scalpel or any other flat, sharp object

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:33.000
Be careful not to go too far

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:44.000
If you have the camera pack lid, we recommend screwing it on before carrying out repairs

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:27.000
Be careful to place it correctly

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:29.000
You must line the holes up with the screws

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:37.000
The black part must fit in the casing element

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:42.000
Press firmly

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:55.000
The small screw goes in at the tip, the two large ones on the sides

